41
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,280
(As expected.)

42
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:50,360
(My future father-in-law is a Fighter
obsessed with martial arts.)

43
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:52,270
(He shouldn't be hard
to get along with.)

44
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,880
A hero deserves a treasured saber.

45
00:01:55,390 --> 00:01:57,190
How can it be measured by money?

46
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:59,520
Thank you, Miss.

47
