Why?

48
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:13,700
You lied to me!

49
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:15,270
Xu Qi'an, I won't trust you ever again!

50
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:16,550
Get out! Out!

51
00:02:16,550 --> 00:02:18,430
Leave me alone!

52
00:02:19,170 --> 00:02:20,360
I can't stay here anymore!

53
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,550
Not anymore!

54
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:24,240
My family betrayed me!

55
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:25,830
Get out!

56
00:02:25,830 --> 00:02:26,710
Out!

57
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,990
What a nice saber!

58
00:02:28,990 --> 00:02:31,110
You must be Miss Xu Lingyue.

59
