Your brother is right.

60
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,080
You're gorgeous

61
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,150
and elegant.

62
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,150
You're flattering me, Simu.

63
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:40,710
After thinking,

64
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,360
I believe this is perfect for you.

65
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:50,240
Isn't it

66
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,430
