the skin fantastically.

68
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,670
Ms. Li gave me a jar.

69
00:02:57,670 --> 00:02:58,920
It was really good.

70
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:01,240
I waited in line for days
but failed to get another one.

71
00:03:02,110 --> 00:03:03,110
Miss Simu,

72
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,710
it's so sweet of you.

73
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,150
I pulled some strings to get it.

74
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:08,570
That's fine.

75
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:11,430
Such cream is designed for beauties like her.

76
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,590
I'll try it for you.

77
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:17,110
Thanks. It's so thoughtful of you.

78
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:20,550
(Unlike her mother, Miss Xu)

79
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:22,240
(seems more sophisticated.)

80
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,390
(That's good.)

81
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,270
(I can't wait to know more about her.)

82
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,990
Actually,

83
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,040
I have another gift for you.

84
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,990
Does it smell good?

85
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:37,640
This is the latest book of poems.

86
00:03:37,830 --> 00:03:39,550
(Elegant Poems)
You may read it.

87
00:03:39,550 --> 00:03:40,700
(Top Men of the Dafeng 101)

88
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,590
Thanks, Simu.

89
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,830
Who's this curious little girl?

90
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,150
I stopped by the Moon Resto on my way here

91
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:53,430
and picked up goodies for you.

92
00:03:55,110 --> 00:03:56,480
Moon Resto!

93
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,040
Moon Resto!

94
00:04:00,830 --> 00:04:02,670
Little one, thank Miss Wang first.

95
00:04:02,670 --> 00:04:04,640
Thank you, Miss Pretty.

96
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,800
Eat up.

97
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:07,710
I came in haste, underprepared.

98
00:04:07,710 --> 00:04:09,080
I apologize for the humble gifts.

99
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,960
No, no, no. They're too nice!

100
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:12,360
You're wonderful...

101
00:04:12,590 --> 00:04:14,960
You must be thirsty coming all the way here.

102
00:04:15,110 --> 00:04:18,230
I'm sorry for our humble abode
and poor treat.

103
00:04:18,230 --> 00:04:20,150
- Please bear with it.
- Yes.

104
00:04:20,150 --> 00:04:21,320
No, it's great.

105
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:22,710
You have

106
00:04:22,710 --> 00:04:24,120
a beautiful house of class.

107
00:04:24,590 --> 00:04:25,520
After seeing you,

108
00:04:25,590 --> 00:04:28,200
I realized why Xinnian turned out talented,

109
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,710
kind, and pure.

110
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:34,230
That's also true.

111
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:36,230
Other things aside,

112
00:04:36,230 --> 00:04:37,790
my son, Cijiu, has been

113
00:04:37,910 --> 00:04:39,320
studying hard for 18 years.

114
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,760
He is a talent.

115
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:43,320
Once he passes the Spring Exam,

116
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,880
his... his future

117
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,760
will be limitless.

118
00:04:49,470 --> 00:04:50,910
Xu Cijiu,

119
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:54,470
your 18 years of handwork are futile.

120
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:56,470
Your future

121
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:00,270
is ruined.

122
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:03,590
Now, you're a joke in the scholar circles.

123
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,230
How foolish!

124
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:08,520
How stupid!

125
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:12,230
Why did I believe a liar?

126
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:15,560
Or I wouldn't have ended up like this!

127
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,560
If fate hadn't let Xu Xinnian

128
00:05:22,470 --> 00:05:24,120
be born...

129
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,620
Xu Qi'an, say something to comfort me.

130
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,600
Cijiu,

131
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:41,630
let it go.

132
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,520
Have some hot water.

133
00:05:43,590 --> 00:05:45,030
Hot water?

134
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,470
Hot water?

135
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,440
How foolish!

136
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,710
How stupid!

137
00:05:55,710 --> 00:05:58,470
You're a fool, Xu Xinnian!

138
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,270
Sorry,

139
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,270
Xinnian was humiliated earlier

140
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,230
because of me.

141
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:11,150
Don't blame yourself, Miss.

142
00:06:11,350 --> 00:06:14,590
Cijiu's always been obedient,

143
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,320
well-behaved,

144
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,910
and calm.

145
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:19,640
He'd never cross the line

146
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:21,080
or cause others trouble.

147
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,320
- Right?
- Yes, that's true.

148
00:06:24,470 --> 00:06:25,760
Are you sure he's fine?

149
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,600
Of course!

150
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,880
- Don't worry.
- He's fine.

151
00:06:29,470 --> 00:06:30,390
No need to worry!

152
00:06:30,910 --> 00:06:32,150
Don't worry!

153
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,930
Alright then.

154
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,910
If fate hadn't let Xu Xinnian

155
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,710
be born,

156
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,470
the Dafeng would still be

157
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:56,710
in the dark!

158
00:06:57,230 --> 00:06:58,230
Cijiu,

159
00:06:58,790 --> 00:07:00,120
