160
00:07:00,910 --> 00:07:02,960
I'm tired. I need to sleep.

161
00:07:15,650 --> 00:07:17,010
Are you hanging yourself for real?

162
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,680
Alright. Never mind.

163
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,640
I'm sorry. Get down now!

164
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,880
Leave me alone!

165
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,120
You can't die! Get down!

166
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,960
Let me die!

167
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,560
- Knock it off!
- Leave me alone!

168
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,520
Stop!

169
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,740
- Let me die!
- I'm sorry...

170
00:07:29,150 --> 00:07:30,590
Xinnian is in his room.

171
00:07:30,590 --> 00:07:32,440
(Bright and Sunny)

172
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,320
Xinnian!

173
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:36,530
Don't kill yourself, Xinnian...!

174
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,830
He's studying at this time.

175
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:44,760
Let's not interrupt him.

176
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:45,920
Come on.

177
00:07:46,470 --> 00:07:48,830
Miss Simu came all the way here.

178
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:49,910
So what if he's studying?

179
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:51,520
He can continue later.

180
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,590
Is there dust in your eyes?

181
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,680
- Xin...
- Let me die!

182
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:01,710
He's been studious since childhood.

183
00:08:03,150 --> 00:08:04,440
Yes, that's right.

184
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:08,200
"It's never too early to learn."

185
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:09,830
It's better to

186
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,120
let him focus on his study.

187
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:12,230
Yes, she's right.

188
00:08:18,470 --> 00:08:20,150
I'd like to have a word with him.

189
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:34,710
What do you think

190
00:08:34,830 --> 00:08:36,040
about this poem?

191
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:37,920
This line is beautiful.

192
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,280
Hello.

193
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,240
What's up?

194
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,560
- Nothing.
- Nothing.

195
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,590
- Nothing.
- Nothing.

196
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:12,350
Xinnian is busy with his study.

197
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,280
Let's not

198
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,920
disturb him.

199
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:16,950
Sure.

200
00:09:17,710 --> 00:09:18,550
Hold on.

201
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,510
I apologize for my father

202
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,960
for what happened earlier.

203
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,440
But I believe

204
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:36,920
with your talent,

205
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,400
one day,

206
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,960
you'll enter the Cabinet

207
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,040
and become a minister.

208
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,680
You'll go up in the world

209
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:44,160
and achieve your goals.

210
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,590
I see you're studying.

211
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:57,230
I won't disturb you.

212
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,120
I'll

213
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:00,350
come again another day.

214
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:01,630
Sure. No problem.

215
00:10:06,870 --> 00:10:08,160
(Xinnian,)

216
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,230
(I'm sure)

217
00:10:09,230 --> 00:10:10,630
(that after this,)

218
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:12,830
(you'll fall for me.)

219
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:18,150
♪Flowers in the yard♪

220
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:19,930
♪Bloom and wither♪

221
00:10:19,930 --> 00:10:22,450
♪Time goes by♪

222
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:25,260
♪The wind blows through hair under the eave♪

223
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:26,510
Coward.

224
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:29,490
♪Where is the one taking a break from♪

225
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:32,580
♪Stars are outside the window♪

226
00:10:33,590 --> 00:10:34,870
What is

227
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,080
this stone for?

228
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,830
"My heart is like a stone.

229
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:39,500
It can't be moved around."

230
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:41,810
♪Words said every day♪

231
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:43,190
I'm going to bed.

232
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,160
Your Highness,

233
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:56,470
how did it go?

234
00:10:57,350 --> 00:10:59,630
Yang Youde said Father was working

235
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:00,830
and told me to go back.

236
00:11:01,830 --> 00:11:03,320
As the ruler of the state,

237
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,350
he's always busy

238
00:11:04,350 --> 00:11:05,320
with state affairs.

239
00:11:06,230 --> 00:11:07,630
Father is mad at me

240
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:08,830
and avoiding me.

241
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:12,280
I just heard a joke from others.

242
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,470
Would you like to hear it for fun?

243
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,710
Got kicked out of the Personnel?

244
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:24,040
Yes. Many people saw it.

245
00:11:24,230 --> 00:11:27,400
They said Xu Xinnian
covered his belly like a dead fish

246
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,870
and couldn't move for a long while.

247
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,510
How strange!

248
00:11:32,110 --> 00:11:34,560
Xu Qi'an is gallant and smart.

249
00:11:34,710 --> 00:11:36,630
How come his brother is so simple-minded?

250
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,350
How dare he, a student,

251
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,470
go to provoke

252
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:42,320
the Prime Minister who'll decide his career!

253
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:44,120
Your Highness,

254
00:11:44,230 --> 00:11:45,830
you probably don't know

255
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:48,510
that he seems to admire

256
00:11:48,710 --> 00:11:50,750
Prime Minister Wang's daughter.

257
00:11:51,290 --> 00:11:53,750
That's why the Prime Minister fumed.

258
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,590
Xu Xinnian is

259
00:11:55,830 --> 00:11:58,560
a top student at the Yunlu Academy.

260
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,440
He's young and talented.

261
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:04,400
Why was Wang Zhenwen mad?

262
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,800
So what if he's a top student?

263
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:08,510
There are plenty of them in the state.

264
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,960
Xu Xinnian is

265
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,350
of humble birth

266
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:13,800
without an official post or title.

267
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,440
He might be talented,

268
00:12:15,990 --> 00:12:16,830
but

269
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:19,040
compared with Miss Wang,

270
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:21,750
he's a worthless nobody.

271
00:12:26,710 --> 00:12:27,920
Is one's family background

272
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,320
really that important?

273
00:12:30,590 --> 00:12:31,440
Of course.

274
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,930
People should be matched
for marriage in our state.

275
00:12:34,710 --> 00:12:36,710
Miss Wang is the Prime Minister's daughter,

276
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:38,110
while Xu Xinnian is

277
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:39,400
a humble civilian.

278
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:42,350
Other than him,

279
00:12:42,470 --> 00:12:44,560
even Mr. Xu, who's made great contributions,

280
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:46,350
doesn't deserve her.

281
00:12:50,590 --> 00:12:51,430
Your Highness!

282
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:55,110
Your Highness, I didn't mean that.

283
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:57,710
I'm saying he's smart and resourceful.

284
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:58,810
He's more than qualified

