- Your Majesty,

576
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,840
Wei Yuan is colluding with court officials.

577
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:43,750
We must stop him.

578
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,360
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

579
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:48,440
Mind your own business.

580
00:25:56,200 --> 00:25:57,600
Had Lord Wei interfered,

581
00:25:57,880 --> 00:26:00,030
His Majesty wouldn't have done nothing.

582
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:01,640
Father knows him too well.

583
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,880
Lord Wei cares about the people.

584
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:05,000
His goal

585
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,360
isn't to rise in court.

586
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:07,640
His ambition

587
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:09,550
isn't to gain power.

588
00:26:35,990 --> 00:26:38,710
I didn't believe the Guardians
could supervise officials.

589
00:26:39,270 --> 00:26:41,470
Turns out, your people are really good.

590
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:45,230
We're simply serving the court.

591
00:26:46,470 --> 00:26:48,750
Why did the Guardians

592
00:26:48,750 --> 00:26:49,750
help me?

593
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:53,550
Grains are eight wen per jin.

594
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:55,070
(Grains are eight wen per jin.)

595
00:26:55,070 --> 00:26:56,920
Brown rice, 12 wen per jin.

596
00:26:58,790 --> 00:27:00,550
Rice, 18 wen per jin.

597
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,070
At this time two years ago,

598
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:09,070
paddy rice was only four wen per jin.

599
00:27:09,990 --> 00:27:12,230
Brown rice was six wen per jin.

600
00:27:14,120 --> 00:27:14,960
Lord Wei,

601
00:27:16,030 --> 00:27:17,510
if you want to talk about prices,

602
00:27:17,510 --> 00:27:18,550
go to my place.

603
00:27:19,510 --> 00:27:21,160
We can discuss them all night.

604
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:23,960
This year,

605
00:27:24,550 --> 00:27:26,360
prices have shockingly doubled.

606
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:30,600
The past few years have been eventful.

607
00:27:31,790 --> 00:27:32,840
With war in the North

608
00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:34,200
and droughts in the South,

609
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:37,600
the Treasury has almost been emptied.

610
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:40,880
Despite huge pressure from the Palace,

611
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,750
I didn't raise this year's farm tax.

612
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:45,920
But that didn't change anything.

613
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:50,710
In times of peace,

614
00:27:50,990 --> 00:27:51,960
prices are low.

615
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:53,990
In times of chaos,

616
00:27:54,120 --> 00:27:55,200
farmland is abandoned.

617
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,200
Roads are blocked.

618
00:27:56,270 --> 00:27:57,270
Prices rise.

619
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,990
As powerful officials,

620
00:28:00,070 --> 00:28:01,470
we're concerned about the people,

621
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,480
but

622
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,600
we can't imagine how hard their lives are.

623
00:28:05,550 --> 00:28:08,440
There are people struggling in poverty
in the capital.

624
00:28:09,070 --> 00:28:10,270
In this world,

625
00:28:10,270 --> 00:28:11,790
how many civilians

626
00:28:12,470 --> 00:28:14,990
would be ground like rice

627
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:17,040
but

628
00:28:18,070 --> 00:28:19,310
suffer in silence?

629
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,750
You're benevolent and selfless.

630
00:28:27,310 --> 00:28:28,840
I was narrow-minded.

631
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,070
Prime Minister Wang.

632
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:41,030
After you, Lord Wei.

633
00:28:59,030 --> 00:29:00,120
I helped you

634
00:29:01,130 --> 00:29:02,790
because I saw

635
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:04,840
that facing overwhelming pressure

636
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:06,640
and His Majesty's wrath,

637
00:29:07,610 --> 00:29:09,120
you held on to your principles

638
00:29:09,750 --> 00:29:11,310
and spoke for the people.

639
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:12,760
That's why

640
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:16,120
I'm entrusting this huge task to you.

641
00:29:18,360 --> 00:29:19,230
Lord Wei,

642
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:21,030
what is it?

643
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:23,640
The Witcher's Sect is rampant in the North,

644
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,790
slaughtering civilians.

645
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:26,550
I'll

646
00:29:27,070 --> 00:29:28,510
petition His Majesty

647
00:29:28,930 --> 00:29:30,360
to attack that sect soon.

648
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:32,760
Then

649
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:35,230
I can only rely on you

650
00:29:36,140 --> 00:29:37,960
to safeguard the court

651
00:29:39,310 --> 00:29:40,710
and the Dafeng.

652
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:19,580
(...the people.)

653
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:24,440
Looking up,

654
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:26,920
one can face the heavens.

655
00:30:27,230 --> 00:30:28,120
Look down,

656
00:30:28,470 --> 00:30:30,070
one won't disappoint the people.

657
00:30:35,310 --> 00:30:36,150
Sir,

658
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:38,160
Silver Gong Guardian,
Xu Qi'an, came to see you.

659
00:30:38,900 --> 00:30:40,360
(Personnel)
Without permission,

660
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:42,200
the Guardians can't enter the Personnel.

661
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:43,400
You should leave.

662
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,840
Hold on.

663
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:46,360
I'm Xu Qi'an,

664
00:30:46,470 --> 00:30:47,640
Xu Xinnian's elder brother

665
00:30:47,790 --> 00:30:49,540
- Greetings.
- and a Silver Gong Guardian.

666
00:30:49,840 --> 00:30:50,750
Silver Gong!

667
00:30:51,470 --> 00:30:53,710
Lord Wei sent me here for investigation.

668
00:30:53,790 --> 00:30:55,640
You... Did I not make myself clear?

669
00:30:56,030 --> 00:30:57,160
I'll say it again.

670
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,680
The Personnel is off-limits.

671
00:30:58,680 --> 00:31:00,300
Without His Majesty's edict, the Guardians

672
00:31:00,300 --> 00:31:01,470
aren't allowed in.

673
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:03,030
Please leave.

674
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,150
Sir,

675
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,550
do us a favor

676
00:31:06,790 --> 00:31:07,640
and let us in.

677
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,440
Do you a favor?

678
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:10,350
Alright.

679
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,530
Fine. Close the gate.

680
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:12,390
Hey...

681
00:31:13,990 --> 00:31:14,920
My hand...

682
00:31:16,470 --> 00:31:18,230
- Never mind.
- Let me go!

683
00:31:18,230 --> 00:31:19,230
I have other plans.

684
00:31:24,470 --> 00:31:25,750
You're too slow.

685
00:31:25,750 --> 00:31:26,880
I've waited for a while.

686
00:31:27,230 --> 00:31:28,200
It occurred to me

687
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,680
that I shouldn't have worn my uniform

688
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:30,840
to work with a civilian.

689
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,030
It wouldn't be of help.

690
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:35,310
What's Wang Zhenwen doing?

691
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:38,290
A drop in need shall be returned
with a spring in deed, no?

692
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:39,400
Look at that petty official.

693
00:31:39,710 --> 00:31:40,840
As low-ranking as he is,

694
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:42,550
he's so bureaucratic.

695
00:31:42,710 --> 00:31:43,550
By the way,

696
00:31:43,710 --> 00:31:44,960
why did you stop me just now?

697
00:31:45,040 --> 00:31:45,880
Had you let me go,

698
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:47,460
I would've turned that place upside down!

699
00:31:47,710 --> 00:31:48,550
Calm down.

700
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:50,310
I've sent a message

701
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,840
to ask Miss Wang for help.

702
00:31:51,840 --> 00:31:52,680
Really?

703
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,040
Fine.

704
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:55,960
I'm off.

705
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:57,960
Where are you going?

706
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:58,880
Let's talk.

707
00:31:58,880 --> 00:31:59,820
About what?

708
00:31:59,820 --> 00:32:01,220
If I need you, I'll send Su Su over.

709
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:04,710
Have you paid?

710
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:07,960
Sir,

711
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,070
put it on my tab.

712
00:32:09,230 --> 00:32:10,070
Sure.

713
00:32:18,750 --> 00:32:19,590
Hey, little boy.

714
00:32:19,790 --> 00:32:20,710
Give me my pouch.

715
00:32:20,710 --> 00:32:22,200
Your pouch? Can you prove it?

716
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:24,030
Finders keepers.

717
00:32:25,120 --> 00:32:27,230
A gold sunflower seed is in it

718
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:28,680
with the character "Zhi".

719
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:29,640
Open it and look.

720
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,030
Give it back!

721
00:32:33,070 --> 00:32:34,960
- Give it to me.
- What are you doing?

722
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,360
- Picking a fight?
- It's mine.

723
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:37,550
- Do you know me?
- Give it

724
00:32:37,550 --> 00:32:38,550
- Don't push me.
- back.

725
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:40,120
- It's my pouch.
- It's not yours.

726
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:40,990
It's mine.

727
00:32:40,990 --> 00:32:42,200
It's my pouch.

728
00:32:42,270 --> 00:32:45,510
(Mu Nanzhi)
How did you know a gold sunflower seed

729
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,680
was in it with the character "Zhi"?

730
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:49,510
It's my pouch.

731
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,880
Of course I know.

732
00:32:50,990 --> 00:32:52,200
Your pouch?

733
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,920
There's a character "Zhi",

734
00:32:55,270 --> 00:32:57,750
but it's not on a gold sunflower seed.

735
00:33:02,230 --> 00:33:04,780
(Pig.)
(It says "Pig".)

736
00:33:05,230 --> 00:33:06,270
I knew it.

737
00:33:06,270 --> 00:33:07,790
No wonder I was so unlucky

738
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:11,360
that I lost a pouch every time I hung out.

739
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:16,600
So all those pouches

740
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,470
were taken by you, pig!

741
00:33:19,270 --> 00:33:20,110
(Looks like)

742
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:21,640
(she's that unlucky victim.)

743
00:33:21,990 --> 00:33:23,790
Miss, he stole your pouch.

744
00:33:23,790 --> 00:33:25,920
- I saw everything.
- Really?

745
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,230
You have to believe me.

746
00:33:27,230 --> 00:33:28,510
He even beat me.

747
00:33:28,990 --> 00:33:29,880
You little liar!

748
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:30,720
What's wrong?

749
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:32,550
Whose pouch is it?

750
00:33:35,360 --> 00:33:36,470
I get it.

751
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:38,640
You two are

752
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:40,070
setting me up

753
00:33:40,070 --> 00:33:41,960
in public in broad daylight.

754
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,310
You're partners in fraud, right?

755
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,070
Let's go to the authorities.

756
00:33:45,070 --> 00:33:45,910
Are you coming?

757
00:33:45,990 --> 00:33:46,830
No.

758
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,400
- Yes or no?
- I didn't say anything.

759
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,750
I saw nothing.

760
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:51,470
Stop it.

761
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:52,440
Your partner ran away.

762
00:33:52,550 --> 00:33:53,550
Will you go with me?

763
00:33:53,990 --> 00:33:54,830
I...

764
00:33:56,360 --> 00:33:57,710
I... I'll let it slide this time.

765
00:33:58,510 --> 00:33:59,400
But next time,

766
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,310
I'll make you pay!

767
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:06,880
I made it.

768
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:08,670
Here you go, 600 liang.

769
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:10,200
Thanks.

770
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:22,820
(Looking up, one can face the heavens...)

771
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:25,470
Your writing has further improved, Father.

772
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:28,190
It can literally be seen from the back.

773
00:34:28,470 --> 00:34:29,470
How powerful.

774
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:32,670
You wrote,

775
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:34,800
"Looking up, one can face the heavens.

776
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:36,650
Looking down,
one won't disappoint the people."

777
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:40,470
But that's not how you've been acting lately.

778
00:34:44,150 --> 00:34:45,880
What do you mean?

779
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:47,550
What's your point?

780
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,240
Let me be clear.

781
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:52,720
If you're here for that Guardian Xu,

782
00:34:53,150 --> 00:34:53,990
don't bother

783
00:34:54,240 --> 00:34:55,510
to say it.

784
00:34:55,570 --> 00:34:56,410
Why?

785
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:57,990
Do you feel guilty?

786
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:00,240
Father,

787
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,920
you know

788
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,590
you owe the Xu Family.

789
00:35:03,990 --> 00:35:05,400
If you keep avoiding them,

790
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:06,840
can you face the heavens?

791
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:07,880
Won't you disappoint them?

792
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:11,110
The Xu brothers

793
00:35:11,360 --> 00:35:13,190
are in cahoots.

794
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:14,800
Mu,

795
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:16,720
you're a clever girl.

796
00:35:17,190 --> 00:35:19,920
You weren't fooled
by their ruse of self-injury, were you?

797
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:24,150
You're right, Father.

798
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,670
I saw through

799
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:27,470
Xinnian's silly trick,

800
00:35:28,470 --> 00:35:29,960
but I also saw

801
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:32,590
he went this far for me.

802
00:35:33,070 --> 00:35:34,400
He was sincere.

803
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,760
Although he played a trick,

804
00:35:37,240 --> 00:35:38,190
he made me happy.

805
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,280
I wouldn't mind.

806
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:42,550
Besides, he did so

807
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:44,400
to change your opinion on him.

808
00:35:44,470 --> 00:35:45,990
To change my opinion,

809
00:35:48,550 --> 00:35:50,400
he has to pass the Spring Exam first.

810
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:51,880
That won't happen soon.

811
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:53,720
Father, you haven't told me

812
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:55,280
why you refuse to help the Xu Family.

813
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:57,320
If you're so ungrateful,

814
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:59,360
won't others look down on the Wang Family?

815
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:04,440
The Personnel is off-limits.

816
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:08,320
Ever since I became
the Vice Minister there 14 years ago,

817
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:11,360
not one Guardian has been
allowed in the archive.

818
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:15,110
No exceptions since the Dafeng was founded.

819
00:36:18,990 --> 00:36:19,830
Well,

820
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:22,470
they don't

821
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,190
have to go inside.

822
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:30,110
Y-Y-You...

823
00:36:30,110 --> 00:36:33,360
Some chicken soup you made.

824
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:39,240
Alright, I'm full.

825
00:36:41,550 --> 00:36:42,390
Take this.

826
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:45,960
This Healing Powder is fantastic

827
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:48,150
and extremely rare.

828
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:50,390
Father,

829
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,470
who is it for?

830
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:54,760
Your injured admirer, Xu.

831
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:05,560
Mr. Chu.

832
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:07,800
I'm late. My apologies.

833
00:37:10,340 --> 00:37:11,380
Sorry to keep you waiting.

834
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,150
How did it go?

835
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:17,190
Don't get me started.
A geezer fooled us.

836
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:19,280
Good liquor!

837
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:22,150
This 30-year-old liquor

838
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:23,400
tastes rich and strong.

839
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,070
Let's set aside the troubles.

840
00:37:25,510 --> 00:37:26,350
Why not

841
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:28,190
indulge in drinks?

842
00:37:29,070 --> 00:37:30,110
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

843
00:37:36,280 --> 00:37:37,120
Here we go.

844
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,120
Ouch!

845
00:37:45,080 --> 00:37:46,920
Bear with it.

846
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:48,240
Easy!

847
00:37:48,990 --> 00:37:49,830
Just stop.

848
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:50,720
It's nothing serious.

849
00:37:50,720 --> 00:37:51,560
I'm fine.

850
00:37:51,590 --> 00:37:52,840
Nothing serious?

851
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:55,630
I only hit you once.

852
00:37:55,630 --> 00:37:56,920
How come you were badly injured?

853
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,630
Who left all those scratches?

854
00:37:59,990 --> 00:38:01,990
I hit myself a few more times.

855
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:07,110
But I was badly injured for nothing.

856
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:10,110
We didn't get to see Prime Minister Wang.

857
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:14,150
I made a bad plan.

858
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,400
Let me put more powder on you.

859
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:16,390
Don't bother.

860
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:19,150
I realized something yesterday.

861
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:21,470
With Prime Minister Wang's experience,

862
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:23,190
he must've seen through

